creator: VOODOO
descriptionHtml:
Get your net worth to the moon!
First, play rock-paper-scissors to decide to goes first, then grow your money stack by picking up the best cards, make sure you have more money than your opponent.
Simply tap a card to use it!
Don't forget about red cards, you can reduce your opponent stack by using them, but so can do your opponent so be careful.
descriptionShort: select correct cards and become the richest
